nhc_headline: ...DESPITE JERRY'S CENTER MOVING NORTH, FLOODING RAINS CONTINUE OVER PORTIONS OF THE LEEWARD ISLANDS...
summary: ...DESPITE JERRY'S CENTER MOVING NORTH, FLOODING RAINS CONTINUE OVER PORTIONS OF THE LEEWARD ISLANDS... As of 8:00 AM AST Fri Oct 10 the center of Jerry was located near 19.8, -63.3 with movement NW at 17 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
